column17: Požiadavka na minimálny vek na vysielanie LIVE
column18: Ak chceš mať účet na TikToku, musíš mať viac ako 18 rokov a ak chceš vysielať LIVE, musíš mať {age} rokov a viac. Zaviazali sme sa dôsledne zabezpečiť, aby platforma TikTok predstavovala pre osoby mladšie ako 18 rokov bezpečnú a pozitívnu skúsenosť. Ak zistíme, že niekto nedosiahol minimálny vek na TikToku, zakážeme mu účet. Ak sa dozvieme, že niekto nespĺňa minimálny vek na vysielanie LIVE, zakážeme mu prístup k vysielaniu LIVE. column3: Video not eligible for recommendation in the For You feed
column18: We maintain content eligibility standards for the For You feed (FYF) that prioritize safety and are informed by the diversity of our community and cultural norms. We make ineligible for the FYF certain content that may not be appropriate for a broad audience related to: (1) Behavioral Health, (2) Sensitive and Mature Themes, (3) Integrity and Authenticity, and (4) Regulated Goods. Content that is ineligible for the FYF can still be discovered in other ways, such as through search tools or by following an account.We proactively enforce our Community Guidelines through a mix of technology and human moderation. We have detected this policy violation using automated measures. We have used automated measures in making this decision.
column30: The decision was taken pursuant to own-initiative investigations.
